** QuickStart **

- If you don't have Gradle, run:
	'sh gradlew' or 
	'gradlew.bat'

- To generate the relevant project files run:
    'gradle eclipse' or 
    'gradle idea'

- To build the distribution run:
	'gradle kittyDist'


** Gradle **

Apache Kitty uses the Gradle build system.

If you don't have Gradle installed, run the 'gradlew' or 'gradlew.bat' script
to download and install Gradle on your system.

You can then run 'gradle tasks' to see a list of the tasks in this build.
The tasks labelled in this format: 'kittyXxxxx' are Apache Kitty specific tasks.



** Gradle Eclipse Plugin **

Download and install the Gradle Eclipse plugin to get build integration in the 
Eclipse IDE.  More information, here:

 http://static.springsource.org/sts/docs/2.7.0.M1/reference/html/gradle/index.html








